{"tid":728173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個廣告做乜撚野","createTime":"2018-07-03T15:06:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T10:14:53.000Z","uid":31359,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3997cd7d8b0491c0e263f06b366a4187655bf561","tid":728173,"uid":31359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:06:39.000Z","msg":"近排成日睇世界盃見到呢個廣告<br />\n大約就係有個亞洲人有個鬼佬fd叫佢睇波<br />\n但同時佢老婆又叫佢幫佢個囡買生日會d野<br />\n最後唔知搵間乜柒速遞物流搞掂曬<br />\n<br />\n問題嚟喇 最後佢個女出鏡發現竟然係mix<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時驟眼睇都已經feel到成部電視機綠光四射<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先唔講兩公婆明明講緊廣東話 無厘頭加個鬼佬入去成件事好唔自然<br />\n最後仲要整個混血種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 度橋條友係咪鬼佬嚟，特登想笑鳩亞洲男性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q-A0vbxI6Ww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ-A0vbxI6Ww&d=1m7KRwVCeMbAbSeVDOwjK7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=54383158\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q-A0vbxI6Ww</a>"},{"pid":"14a5461062ec160f98cf1fe2821094fcb875f54e","tid":728173,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"thanks dad you're the best<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09432e82e0f84c24c86d7576ba631f3f64673b99","tid":728173,"uid":31359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14a5461062ec160f98cf1fe2821094fcb875f54e","tid":728173,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:09:06.000Z","msg":"thanks dad you're the best<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"其實個鬼佬好惡咁樣問where are you<img src=\"/assets/faces